description: On and Off bursts designed to improve your neuromuscular power and FTP at the same time. 10 minute warm-up level 2 with 3 x 1 minute fast pedals >110rpm.Do 3 x 10 minutes, Micro-bursts,  15 seconds ON at 150% of FTP and 15 seconds OFF at 50% of FTP.  Repeat for entire 10minutes, rest for 5minutes between each set.  It's important that you maintain 90 rpm for both the ON and the OFF periods. Cool-down.
